data.description: Back on the market due to buyer’s financing falling through. Home inspection has been completed and is available to perspective buyers. 2022 HVAC and 2019 water heater—inspections completed. Radon mitigation system recently installed. Fully remodeled kitchen with quartz countertops. Newer appliances throughout. Top of the line remote fireplace to warm up on those winter nights. High quality LVP installed on main level with newer carpeting throughout. Sought after Mounds View School District. Corner lot on a beautiful pond make for relaxing evenings on your porch or deck. Few homes in New Brighton have such a practical layout with 4 bedrooms up, 4 bathrooms throughout, and a large recreational and hobby room in the basement. A 5th and 6th bedroom could be easily added in basement. Expansive owner’s suite with private bathroom, including a whirlpool tub, separate shower, and spacious walk-in closet. Public Park and tennis courts nearby. This home is definitely one to see!
